description:
Whenever I have a conversation with a true Covid-believer ... I always get the same response. People are dying!!!!!! 😏Oh really? Do you know them? No ... Have you seen it with your own eyes? No ... Do you know that last year people died? Yes ... So is it a surprise that this year people die too? At this point they are usually pissed ...😂So you just believe it because the news said so?? Interesting .... 🧐And that’s the end of the conversation ...🤣😂🤣#goodtalk
